Beloved, when you’re agitated and stressed up, you’ll end up being confused not knowing what to do. Reason why you must learn to rest. Apply these practical tools to keep your mind stayed on Jesus. #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive
Beloved, learn to thank God for what He has done in your life. Offer unto Him a sacrifice of praise. Hebrews 13:15 #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive
How to operate in Rest; • Have an attitude of Thanksgiving to God! Give thanks to God. There’s power in thanksgiving. Learn to give thanks. Psalms 34:1-2; John 11:41 #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive

Praying in tongues helps our weaknesses and limitations. Many times, we don’t know the right words or language to use, neither do we have the right articulation of what we want to pray about. Romans 8:26-28 #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive

How to operate in Rest; • Praying in the Holy Spirit (tongues). Speaking in tongues is a gift of Grace and it is a powerful tool that does damage to the kingdom of darkness. It is a mystery that is refreshing. Isaiah 28:11-12 #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive

Philemon 1:6 “That the communication of thy faith may become effectual by the acknowledging of every good thing which is in you in Christ Jesus.” - • All that Christ died to give you, you receive its manifestation by acknowledging that you have it! #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive

Child of God, learn to declare what God has freed you from! Psalms 107:2 — Let the redeemed of the Lord SAY SO! If God has delivered you, declare it to the glory of God and the defeat/shame of the adversary! #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive

How to operate in Rest; • Speak what you believe! Believe what your spirit is saying, even if your mind doesn’t align with it. In not too distant time, your mind will align with your Spirit. #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive

Child of God, never change your confession of faith; it doesn’t matter what the devil shows you, as long as you don’t change your confession, then you have not agreed with him. Hebrews 10:23 #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive

How to operate in Rest; • Let your words agree with what you’re expecting from God. This is very important because I guarantee you that the enemy will paint pictures to make you change your confession. #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive

Heb. 12:2 “Looking unto Jesus the author and finisher of our faith; who for the joy that was set before him endured the cross, despising the shame, and is set down at the right hand of the throne of God.” - Consistently see Jesus by beholding the Word. #TREM #PFL #Rest #BMOLive
